title: Spacious well proportioned one bedroom apartment.  Walk to train.
posting_body: ['No appointments till end of May .', 'Spacious well proportioned one bedroom apartment.', 'Top floor in a two family house.', 'Windowed separate kitchen and windowed bathroom.', 'Your own private staircase and a hallway which gives you a feeling of living in a house.', 'Brand new hardwood floors in the living room and bedroom.', 'Nice clean and comfortable.', 'Good light.', 'Square rooms.', 'Bathroom has a brand new vanity, sink, cabinet and mirror and toilet.', 'It has a shower and a bathtub.', 'Kitchen is windowed and will have a brand new stove and brand new refrigerator.', 'Excellent location half a block to Woodhaven boulevard and few blocks to Juniper Valley Park as well as to Queens boulevard and walking distance to the subway.', 'Plenty of buses in the area plus shopping, restaurants, cafes and major retailers.', 'Easy access to Jackie Robinson and Grand Central as well as LIE.', 'If you are interested in this apartment or any of my other strictly exclusive Astoria, Woodside, Ridgewood, Bushwick, Glendale, and Middle Village listings, please contact Andrusha by replying to this post.', 'Please feel free to provide any information you consider pertinent to your search.', 'Ridgewood Based Independent Broker.', 'Representing strictly hands on local owners of small buildings and houses.', 'No large buildings or impersonal managements.', 'Andrea (Andrusha) Bohackova', 'Licensed Real Estate Broker', 'Sales Rentals Property Management', 'Manhattan Queens Brooklyn', '917-291-2149', '<URL>', '<URL>', '<URL>']
